ComicInfo.Summary:
Framing sequence: pages 1-3;21-24: The original Supreme finds himself on a world that appears to be Earth with no memory of how he got there. Meanwhile the new Supreme finds himself turned into a woman!
The Past is Prelude to the Present: While Supreme seeks revenge against Chi, the employer of Vergessen, he confronts his past sins.
